channel.title: Quick Question
channel.description:
I was on some other forums, in the tutorial section. And I came upon " Make your PC Faster! ".
I'm not going to go into detail, but, I wasn't sure if it was OK for your PC.
They said to put this... [code]page buffer=100000kbps load=100000kbps Download=100000kbps save=100000kbps back=100000kb[/code]
In your [code]system.ini[/code].
Is this OK?
